Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We're Alright! We're Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:24.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}笑一個吧 明天會是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:29.25,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}跳一個 大家一起跳起來
