Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日本向新基地送出物資的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通過DROMLAN 也給我們送來了這些補充物資
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:44.82,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※DROMLAN\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}毛德皇后地航空網路項目，是由南極洲東部建立基地的11個國家簽署的，借用兩個考察站{\r}\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}（挪威特羅爾站、俄羅斯新拉扎列夫站）的長距離冰跑道，作為國際飛機中轉站的合作交通協議。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們的資材就算齊全了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要今年立刻搭建起觀星天文台 還是天方夜譚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過只要有心堅持 花上幾年時間估計…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們得去那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少所有人都是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那是貴子斷絕音信的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老媽肯定把照片傳遍SNS了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不也很好嗎 這樣還能宣傳我們的轉播呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…我的也麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賀年卡只寫給店長一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才那幾個朋友不用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 雖說是賀年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也要等到船回到日本後才能送到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去一下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有那麼痛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是不是在緊張啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨也要去上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以可以帶我們參與海冰和地質的調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會準備攝影機的 你要想好怎麼報導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}探險探險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說要做報導的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不管你等一下情不情願啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向 就是剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才只是測試 所以不算欠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點 馬上就要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三年前就一起做過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰叫貴子前輩什麼都想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 她到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 你媽媽還來過這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個拿來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這下面都是冰塊 所以要用蒸汽熱個洞出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有 我們去的應該是倫灣角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(830,650)\clip(726,610,936,660)}（Rundvågshetta）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這名字聽起來就好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是個岩石裸露的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是你找信惠 她可能願意帶你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是海冰組
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地質組的信惠小姐聽得到嗎 請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聯繫不上 聖誕之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大前年收到的石榴石…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾燥的岩石 和乾涸的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收不到郵件 冷淡的阿優
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在無法聯絡 請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊 這溫差好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別弄我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們看 好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極好壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從這個角度看很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天空在眼前流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道能不能看到極光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要到晚上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我們在的這段時間 不會有夜晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有沒有什麼煩心事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煩心事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空氣太乾燥 嘴唇都乾巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}護唇膏也凍得硬邦邦的 很難塗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}的確很難受 感覺都要脫皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.73,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戶外隊員請立刻回到基地中央區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或是到有應急食品的建築內避難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全沒改善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還是放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說報瀨人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才有人問她會不會打麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的 她會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺很有趣 我也在她背後觀摩了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人字旁加個五讀作什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}準備好的白板正好湊一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是準備好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個鳥好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「滾出去！」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不就問她幾句嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨本來就心胸狹隘嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.36,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\an5\fs30\1c&H767876&\frx328\fry14\pos(998,114)\frz333.8}封鎖名單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.36,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H7262CA&\frz333.5\frx328\fry2\pos(522,482)}刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.36,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&HAD9981&\pos(450,618)\frz331\frx340\fry4}解除封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}門清混一色 雙南風 寶牌3 16000點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不會小時候就跟貴子一起圍著牌桌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 偶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不玩了不玩了 不可能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:33.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\fsp35\fs150\1c&H3725E9&\t(0,2500,0\fs70)\move(384,4,534,42,33,2619)}麻將帝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對手竟然是吟和貴子的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三宅在這嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概在洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她朋友發了封電郵到基地來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朋友？
