Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也沒寄到基地這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明說好每天發郵件的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:09.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs90\1c&H836B65&\be2\move(82,346,-610,512,0,2998)\frx354\fry4\frz13.29}【致三宅日向】羽生第三高中田徑隊全體
