Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.15,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs80\1c&H48404A&\b0\be1\t(0,1740,0\fs45)\move(114,482,330,448,36,1704)}對不起三宅同學 讓你這麼孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是寄給日向的郵件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就這樣擅自打開來看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為…因為我很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你一個人不知道在生什麼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是卻什麼都不說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來你看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好把話說清楚啊 不然我會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怕你是不是隱瞞了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怕你是不是有什麼話說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:14.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs60\1c&H836B65&\b0\be2\frx346\fry330\frz342.1\fscx80\fscy105\pos(185.999,418.001)}對不起三宅同學 讓你這麼孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}醜話說在前頭 這可不是什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我本來不想提 你們聽了也不會好受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夠了 快點說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}簡單來說 就是我退出社團的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然是大會 絕對是讓跑得快的上場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟什麼年級的無關啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是高三的學姐這次大賽後就要引退了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這種原因放水 才是對她們不敬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}200公尺 三宅日向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們沒跟那個笨蛋說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說了啊 都叫她看看臉色了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那一瞬間 我覺得什麼都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那怎麼可能 明明都是她們的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人真的很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她們就是明白這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才想盡辦法把錯推到我頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我退隊 還亂傳我的閒話和謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道這就是你退學的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉我就是條喪家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那發信過來的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 那時候的隊友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說想在轉播時跟我說幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她們說朋友能去南極 自己也很驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才想到「呵呵 我們原來是朋友啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼？和你們的想像有出入？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺這裡都不像是地球了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎？啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好神奇的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們去對面搭帳篷和設置天線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要糾結到什麼時候啊 快忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這樣害我都覺得不舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得我為什麼要來南極？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這裡一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和無拘無束的人們去一無所有的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們看 景色這麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冰 地層 雪水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一個都是不曾看過的顏色和形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有任何我們知道的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡有著和以往完全不一樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是為了享受這一切才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們這樣不就浪費了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 那就把它忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先去紮營 紮營
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可不是在玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才沒有浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定不會浪費這一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟科幻電影一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要喝點水看看 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}某種意義上而言 可能是全世界最乾淨的水了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幾乎沒有被人觸碰過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氣溫也沒有高到能讓細菌繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的耶 冰冰涼涼的好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滋潤身心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨要喝看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等再說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聯繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說句話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是倫灣角的小淵澤 請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 這裡是昭和 信號良好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}景色如何 請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 感覺像是被蛋糕包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子也說過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抵達的那一刻喊說「想吃巧克力蛋糕！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽也……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最棒的天然水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理很擅長些怪工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一點也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能從衛星上看到這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 這是給拍衛星照等特殊情況定位用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會非常清晰的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在沒在拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿優
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿優
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.28,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:20.08,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用管她 她每次都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種地方都有標記 肯定有人在看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可沒話中有話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是極樂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為溫度越來越低了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有更厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等下一鍋水滾了 就做煎蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的很喜歡煎蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在新加坡吃早餐時 也吃了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去打水 你陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不夠用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 是我用掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}風吹起來真的超冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我也會有點想死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果跟日向有同樣的遭遇會怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:31.44,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs60\1c&H836B65&\b0\be2\frx346\fry330\frz342.1\fscx80\fscy105\pos(185.999,418.001)}對不起三宅同學 讓你這麼孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遭遇了這麼過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但某天 又若無其事地聯絡自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為她們所犯下無可挽回的錯而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不可能保持平靜 不可能笑得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨又不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把手套撿起來 給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨老管閒事真是煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 我可能還是挺害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說了 只要手就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你帶我一起來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煎蛋做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H778285&\pos(904,84)\frz344.9\frx348\fry16}可選的過年蕎麥麵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H778285&\frx348\fry16\pos(908,202)\frz349.1}加天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H778285&\frx348\fry16\pos(928,296)\frz353.3}加年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H585A5A&\frx348\fry16\frz353.3\pos(912,368)}純蕎麥麵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}切得真爛 這是刀削麵啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夠細了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重桿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從桿麵開始啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}10分鐘後就正式來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結果曬痕還是沒消
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這說明你在南極玩得很嗨呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是原諒她們 會輕鬆些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想原諒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果原諒了能輕鬆點就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但想像道完歉 她們鬆了一口氣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就一肚子火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「真他媽的」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的肚量也夠小的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是上午9點 和日本有6個小時的時差
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正式開始前 我能說一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 你們能別纏著三宅日向了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是因為你們 日向才退學 飽受艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們可能覺得她恨你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:06.64,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}深夜零時の地平線　広がる世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.98,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今日がずっと眩しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:21.70,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}鼻の奥がツンとした　きれいできれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:26.24,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}胸が痛くなるほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:35.88,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}両手いっぱいありったけの人に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:46.68,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}意味なんかないって言われ続けたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:59.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}宇宙(そら)から届くひかり　逆さまの星空見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:03.11,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:11.70,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}さあ　迷いなんて置き去りにして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:18.08,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}探しに行くんだ　見果てぬ世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:26.18,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}勇気出して　進んでいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:06.64,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}眼前是深夜零點的地平線 一片廣大的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.98,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今天一直是那麼耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:21.70,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我激動得鼻尖一癢 眼前的景象是那麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:26.24,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}燦爛到叫我心口作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:35.88,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}許許多多的人 裝滿雙手也擠不下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:46.68,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}都在勸我不要白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:59.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只是仰頭看見那顛倒的星空 灑下的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:03.11,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我會從這裡揚帆啟航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:11.70,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}把心裡的迷茫留在岸邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:18.08,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}去探索廣闊無垠 斑斕神秘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:26.18,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要拿出勇氣 走出大大的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能覺得她每天會想起田徑隊而掉眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向現在和我們過得極其開心而充實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}享受著你們留在日本絕對體驗不到的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向已經積極地邁出了腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我們一同邁開了腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多棒啊 這才是友情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟日向不一樣 個性很差
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們就懷著這份不安的心情活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們傷害別人 帶給別人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就背負著過錯活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是傷人的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是傷害我朋友的代價！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事到如今還想求個心安？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今年很快就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有電視看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然是去年的錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿優！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿優 阿優！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們也來撞掉煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全都撞掉吧 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說不定會撞壞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個鐵桶而已 無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那第一下四個人一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2！
Comment: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:23.86,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:34.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:40.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:51.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:23:02.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:13.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:18.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:24.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:23.86,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:34.74,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:40.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:51.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:23:02.06,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:13.37,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:18.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:24.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
